# Releases: __PROJECT_NAME__

> Updated on: __DATE__

This directory records what was actually delivered in a given version.

## When to record a release

- A new version is published externally
- An internal milestone needs a stable summary snapshot
- The team needs to explain what was added, fixed, or still risky in this version

## Suggested content

- Added items
- Fixed items
- Breaking changes
- Known issues
- Links to related change records, ADRs, and tasks
